Actions.Text: REFERENCE CHANGED TO WAYS AND MEANS

Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to Major Andrew D. Byers
Summary: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to Major Andrew D. Byers on state route 324 in the town of Clarence.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to Major Andrew D. Byers
